Docker image for running a SOAPUI mockservice.
Copyright 2015-2018 Erik-Berndt Scheper and all contributors from the GIT log.

This image is built on the Centos base image, downloads and installs an Oracle JDK and SoapUI.

Furthermore, it includes a demonstration SoapUI project for the Bank BLZ Service (Bank Sort Codes) used by banks in
Germany. The WSDL for this service is hosted at http://www.thomas-bayer.com/axis2/services/BLZService?wsdl.

By using this image, or building your own dockerfile on top of this, you implicitly accept the
license terms of the above products.
